---
import Contact from "./Contact.tsx";
---

<section
  class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-5xl flex-col items-center gap-8 px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 sm:py-12 md:gap-10 md:py-16 lg:px-8"
  aria-labelledby="contact-heading"
>
  <h1
    id="contact-heading"
    class="max-w-[22rem] text-center text-2xl font-extrabold leading-tight sm:max-w-none sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl"
  >
    ¡QUEREMOS SABER DE TI!
  </h1>
  <p
    class="max-w-2xl text-center text-base font-medium leading-relaxed text-gray-800 sm:text-lg md:text-xl"
  >
    Ponte en contacto con nosotros, estaremos encantados de ayudarte en breve.
  </p>

  <div
    class="flex w-full flex-col items-center gap-8 md:flex-row md:items-center md:gap-8 lg:gap-10"
  >
    <img
      src="/contact-side.webp"
      alt=""
      class="h-auto w-full max-w-xs shrink-0 object-contain sm:max-w-sm md:w-1/2 md:max-w-md"
    />
    <div class="w-full min-w-0 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-4 sm:p-6 md:w-1/2">
      <Contact client:load />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
